These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, alhambra
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, july
1. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
2. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##5
3. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Beverage      | tea     | coffee      |
| Cigar          | alhambra | aristoff    |
| Hobby         | chess   | board-games |
| Birthday   | may  | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, iced-tea
There are 2 different favourite colors: lavender, orange
2 different games are played: whist, domino
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, snowmobile
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lavender is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
3. the person playing domino is not to the right of the person playing whist##8
4. the person driving the boat is not the person who likes orange##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk        | iced-tea    |
| Color       | lavender         | orange |
| Game         | domino | whist   |
| Transport   | boat               | snowmobile  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, electrician
2 different games are played: backgammon, whist
There are 2 different nationalities: australian, japanese
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
1. the australian is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is not to the right of the owner of the ferret##8
3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the electrician##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job   | doctor       | electrician |
| Game   | backgammon       | whist    |
| Nationality   | australian | japanese |
| Pet           | cat        | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: singing, sudoku
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, nurse
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: golf, soccer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: musical, action
1. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere to the right of the nurse##5
2. the person who's hobby is singing is not to the left of the person watching action movies##8
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Hobby         | sudoku | singing  |
| Job           | nurse  | designer |
| Sport   | soccer | golf   |
| Movie-Genre     | action   | musical |

