.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: documentary, scientific
2 different pets are kept: chinchilla, bird
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, surfing
City: boston, liverpool
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##8
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
4. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | scientific |
| Pet   | bird    | chinchilla     |
| Sport         | basketball  | surfing    |
| City     | liverpool     | boston       |

