.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-10::.
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, lettuce
There are 2 different favourite colors: chestnut, fuchsia
The people have 2 different jobs:  doctor, software-developer
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water
1. the person eating cabbage is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
4. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
5. the person drinking water is not to the left of the person eating lettuce##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |         2          |
| Food        | cabbage | lettuce            |
| Color       | fuchsia | chestnut              |
| Job         | doctor  | software-developer |
| Beverage   | iced-tea     | water         |

