2. the entrepreneur is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is not the person who growsbellflower##6
4. the person who growsbellflower is not to the right of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
