3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |
| Food          | plum         | corn    |
| Hobby           | sudoku | card-games   |
| Nationality   | australian   | thai    |
| House     | palace         | ranch-style |

 